name: Kelly Slater's Pro Surfer [GBA]
description:
Kelly Slater's Pro Surfer is a sports-arcade game developed by Beenox and HotGen. It came out on 21-08-2002. Aspyr published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Exceptional".
Kelly Slater's Pro Surfer is available on Xbox, GameCube, Game Boy Advance and Classic Macintosh.
